// Principal Component Analysis plugin (pure C++, no external dependency).
// Importing this file loads pca.so and registers the "pca" model method:
//   df[model { ~ x1 + x2 + x3, method = pca, k = 2 }].
// The result / model_fitted give the pc1..pck scores; model_summary gives the
// loadings; model_predict projects new rows onto the trained components.
